title: Music Therapy
description: Music Therapy is for everyone! Drury University staff and students provide opportunities for individuals to participate in music therapy. Pre-registration is required. Contact your Support Coordinator for more information.

title: Project STIR
description: The Missouri Division of Developmental Disabilities regional Advocacy Specialist comes to WC Partners to provide training designed to empower people with developmental disabilities. It provides the practical tools necessary for anyone who is interested in being a self-advocate and leader in making choices and decisions about how they live their lives. This is a six-week program and pre-registration is required.
